Danny recaps this week's explosive new Real Housewives of Potomac, which featured water aerobics, Ashley's arrival, a whiskey tasting with Mr. Copperpots, and the confrontation between Wendy and Gizelle! Danny also touches on his senior prom, the movie Hustlers, and more!
